Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hang out with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I did something\Nthat can't be undone. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now just calm down and tell me why. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I don't want to be a bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Who cares about that now?\NIf there's anything I can do, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say you'd do {\i1}anything{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered I hadn't even {\i1}touched {\i0}that report\NI had for homework over summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same screw-up as last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do college students still\Nget summer homework, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my mom's mad,\Nmy little brother's teasing me--it's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why'd you close the door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:09.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to hang out with you\Nthis summer, help me with my report!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, c'mon! Please? Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:18.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Open up! Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:33.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uzaki-{\i1}chan {\i0}Wants to Hang Out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:54.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Episode 12: Uzaki-{\i1}chan {\i0}Wants to Hang Out More!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hana, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting more comfortable by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you; she must have been\Nhiding her claws way back when.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boss, let me handle the heavy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Threw out your back, huh?\NThat hasn't happened in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll close for today.\NI'll get to the chiropractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has a driver's license?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making an appointment at the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take Dad there in our car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hana, you and I will close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:46.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\i0}could be manager for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll come back to find\Nmy café's been hijacked. Close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Closed"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it compare to Dad's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the depth of flavor in his coffee,\Nbut I like the fresh taste of yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you inherit the café one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherit it? Yeah, I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or... {\i1}take {\i0}it, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why reword it to sound so threatening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be happening anytime soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much I still need\Nto be able to run a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A driver's license, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chiropractic Clinic"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness Sakurai was around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been like that:\Nsurly but accommodating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid to use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a {\i1}tool{\i0}, Hana--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two like in high school, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the swim club together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you flirt--er,\Nhang out then like you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we actually started hanging out\Na little after we started college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! That's a tad surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only saw each other\Nfor club business in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the first time we met--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The swim club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not much of a swimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no--you'd be a manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in any club, are you?\NWe can both join!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know some cute third-years\Nthere from middle school. C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm too chicken to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two first-year\Nmanagers joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after them, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Ugh, pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, we're a pretty big bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy, but do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This third-year manager will show you the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain what you'll be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late. I was cleanin' up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got two new first-year managers today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That's somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet y--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I'm Sakurai. Second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So scary! Those eyes--too fierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We {\i1}have {\i0}upperclassmen like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first day, and I'm ready to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so frightening! Just... yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, yeah, that first impression was the pits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! His eyes never\Nreally bothered me all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as you know, he's a serious,\Nearnest person at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy, Sakurai! That's a new record!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These're heavy. I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for a new record! You can do it, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just so awkward\Nand prone to misunderstandings...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized right away\Nthat he wasn't scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you got friendlier\Nand friendlier with Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even started to talk like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I mean, you haven't\Nbeen talking slangy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? Do you only talk\Nlike that when Sakurai's around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be on my way!\NThat's enough remin... reminiscin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm sorry! I must have touched a nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hadn't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye! I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...seein' ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just dig up a landmine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the greatest treasure around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I've {\i1}got {\i0}to get her to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Senpai like when he's drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized I've never\Nactually seen him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he cry? Laugh?\NGet combative? I can't picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Usually you reveal\Nwhatever you've been holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'd like him\Nto be a strip-naked drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's personal, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai can hold his liquor,\Nso he might not get drunk at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sak's no lightweight, but he {\i1}does {\i0}get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just knows his limits and sticks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! So one of Senpai's rare\Nfriends has seen him drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rare friends"? Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what was he like?\NHow much does he have to put away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you trying to go\Nafter Sak while he's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I hate that {\i1}he's {\i0}seen\N{\i1}my {\i0}booze-related screw-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to drag him down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I think you had it coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, please! This is the perfect time\Nfor scheming, with Senpai off work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't cause {\i1}too {\i0}much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she could cause some {\i1}fun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray! Thanks a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to set up a drinking party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given how it went with you last time,\NAmi, I think I'll go it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Hana's mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever did you do to make\NHana shut you out, daughter of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're here! Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you want to come over\Nto drink all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I finished my report, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you did? Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go all-out today!\NI'll handle the cooking, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The going-home's the hard part with Sak,\Nso he rarely drinks when he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he'll lower\Nhis guard if he's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phase 1: check!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... You really are a great cook, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you could make chili shrimp at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! You're a real pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that {\i0}is an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out spicy snacks with\Na lot of flavor to keep him drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.99,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"They Attack in Packs!"\N"Massive!"\N"The Original Shark Movie!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rented some DVDs, Senpai. Wanna watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got five different killer-shark flicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distract him from his drinking\Nso he won't think about how much he's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phases 2 and 3: check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since Sak tends to match\Nor beat whoever he's with,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if {\i1}you're {\i0}drinking,\Nhe'll naturally keep drinking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend you're drinking... just pretend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Senpai. Have some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the main event, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:32.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't drink too much or\Nmake anyone else drink too much"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Sak's drunk, he's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can hold a conversation of sorts,\Nbut his judgment is way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he starts looking\Nreally sloppy, too. Sloppy Sak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty useless, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\i0}seem happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that state, Sak can't lie--and\Nforget trying to be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mental defenses are zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's big on minding his limits because\Nhe doesn't want to show that side to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do look like\Nyou're feeling no pain, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never even dreamed\Nof this level of vulnerability!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know... thanks... for all your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'd be happier if you could give me\Nyour honest opinions {\i1}without {\i0}the alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do that... too shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been holding back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's your chance to come out\Nwith allll the stuff you couldn't say before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped by to see how it was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I told Uzaki\Nto leave the door unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sak, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuhito? What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I laid out your futon. Get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be under covers, too, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep easy. I'll lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is weird about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she in my futon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he in my futon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So neither of you remember\Nanything about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to come in\Non your day off, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had my suspicions and {\i1}gave {\i0}them today off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, why don't you try remembering\Nthings in order, one by one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One by one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One by one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely remember making dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eating and drinking while we watched movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crazed shark slammed\Ninto the hero of the third movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who then got reincarnated into some other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like, "He's crazy strong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}think {\i0}that's all I can remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of movie is {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that... I enjoyed Senpai's\Npitiful tipsiness for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the sense it was {\i1}extremely {\i0}amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I woke up,\Nwe were in the same futon somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Closed"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologies. Could you say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're listening closely this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about an obvious bribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, Uzaki was beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do {\i1}anything{\i0}!\NI really can't remember at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't remember,\Nyou can't be {\i1}sure {\i0}you didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two really are a pain at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I was there, and I'm saying\Nnothing happened! Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two young people and nothing happened?!\N{\i1}That's {\i0}the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}mad {\i0}at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them, Uzaki!\NYou were up longer than me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so fuzzy. I can't say for sure that I--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you grinning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't actually remember\Nanything from last night, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something definitely happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good. And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is imagine whatever\Nmarvelous event it could have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have joined them--even\Nif I had to force my way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my daughter like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me tag along next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy a guest futon, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you go {\i1}home{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about we do it again today?\NTwo nights in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NClasses start again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Huh" nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha. I see. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break... is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting like it's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you seriously just realize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess... I'll just be\Nsleeping until winter break...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is hanging out the only\Nthing you ever think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hana! Time to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Hana's looking even more dopey than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, Kiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong coffee for\Nyour first day back at college.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perk up a little, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some college student.\NWhat an aggravating big sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:32.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Super Huge"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Uzaki. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually came to campus.\NI was sure you'd whine and moan about it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm still feeling about\N90 percent of that end-of-summer shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not over it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't hang out {\i1}nearly {\i0}enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were always summer,\NI could hang out with you {\i1}so much more{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! You need to\Nconsider a woman's feelings--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be summer.\NWe can hang out whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it, Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No--no, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I {\i1}meant {\i0}was that we still have\Nplenty of time before we graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not... whatever you were thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And whatever {\i1}was {\i0}I thinking, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hang out with me so badly,\NI guess I'll have to oblige!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can thank me now, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! You know what you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying as {\i1}hell{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:13.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uzaki-{\i1}chan {\i0}Wants to Hang Out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Senpai--let's go hang out!